  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Ungraspable, light, free and elusive, this Secret allows the magus to become one with the most difficult element to define and have access to a multiplicity of spells that make them an impossible target.<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>KNOWN SPELLS</strong><br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you choose this secret, you learn the @Compendium[world.spells-historia.syFMHBRvhyPUQR4T]{Gust} and @Compendium[world.spells-historia.16Im3rB8ckLd8t0B]{Blade Ward}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">cantrips, and when you gain a level in the secret you learn the corresponding spells indicated in the following table:<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>Cantrips:</strong> @Compendium[world.spells-historia.syFMHBRvhyPUQR4T]{Gust}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[world.spells-historia.16Im3rB8ckLd8t0B]{Blade Ward}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>1st level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.pub0OWVEB71XQx1n]{Feather Fall}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.IBJmWjzbQGu7M4UX]{Fog Cloud}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>2nd level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.FSMy6VAjDnXY9vWz]{Gust of Wind}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.MRxldJd6C4bsBo3O]{Levitate}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>3rd level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.2IWiZAJtOGDoKjiz]{Gaseous Form}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.dhqBY4TvVjxVmOZd]{Sleet Storm}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>4th level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.da0a1t2FqaTjRZGT]{Freedom of Movement}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.WN2LWEljYU6QqnRH]{Ice Storm}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>5th level: </strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.RpKjTlYASrfqUPVA]{Cone of Cold}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.o9ZCvuD2B1OTcubb]{Wall of Force}<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>MYSTERIES</strong></span><br /><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.YycN5G2TMrBgzM4R]{Founding Mystery: Grace of the Wind}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.qf4Nt3vfNw26wQdU]{Major Mystery: Windy Barrier}</span></p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.HwFWTa9Jnk49E4Th]{Greater Mystery: Whispers in the Breeze}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.VwY24LG7a7dyf7Jp]{Universal Mystery: Walking in the Clouds}</p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>METAMAGIC OF THE SECRET</strong><br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you reach 3rd level in this Secret, you became able to modify the spells they can cast, adapting them to your current needs, and learns the following metamagic options.</span></p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.YrcCraaEBwHHaBuC]{Metamagic: Distant Spell}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.Y4R545k2y1XxS6er]{Metamagic: Extended Spell}</p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
    "source": "Historia Manuale pagina: 148",
